ft\"><div class=\"p-5 border-b border-border bg-slate-50/50 dark:bg-slate-800/50 flex flex-col gap-1 transition-colors\"><h3 class=\"text-sm font-black text-slate-800 dark:text-white flex items-center gap-2\"><span class=\"bg-blue-600 text-white w-5 h-5 rounded flex items-center justify-center text-[12px]\">2</span>기초 단계</h3><p class=\"text-[12px] text-blue-500 font-bold\">&quot;왜 결과가 달라지는지 이해하는 단계&quot;</p></div><div class=\"divide-y divide-border\"><div class=\"p-4 flex items-center justify-between cursor-pointer transition-all bg-blue-600/10 border-r-4 border-blue-600 \"><span class=\"font-bold transition-colors text-xs text-blue-600\">핵심 주제 (Core)</span><div class=\"w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-blue-600\"></div></div><div class=\"flex flex-col\"><div class=\"p-4 flex items-center justify-between cursor-pointer transition-all hover:bg-slate-50 dark:hover:bg-white/5 \"><span class=\"font-bold transition-colors text-xs text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400\">선택형 실습 트랙</span></div><div class=\"bg-slate-50/50 dark:bg-white/5 py-1\"><div class=\"p-4 flex items-center justify-between cursor-pointer transition-all hover:bg-slate-50 dark:hover:bg-white/5 pl-9 py-2.5\"><span class=\"font-bold transition-colors text-[12px] text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400\">트랙 A: 웹 구조 이해</span></div><div class=\"p-4 flex items-center justify-between cursor-pointer transition-all hover:bg-slate-50 dark:hover:bg-white/5 pl-9 py-2.5\"><span class=\"font-bold transition-colors text-[12px] text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400\">트랙 B: 데이터 흐름</span></div><div class=\"p-4 flex items-center justify-between cursor-pointer transition-all hover:bg-slate-50 dark:hover:bg-white/5 pl-9 py-2.5\"><span class=\"font-bold transition-colors text-[12px] text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400\">트랙 C: AI 구조 이해</span></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bg-card rounded-2xl border border-border p-6 space-y-6 shadow-sm transition-colors text-left\"><div class=\"flex justify-between items-center\"><h3 class=\"font-bold text-sm text-slate-800 dark:text-white flex items-center gap-2\"><span class=\"text-lg\">🎁</span> 실습 선택 가이드</h3></div><div class=\"space-y-5\"><div class=\"space-y-2\"><p class=\"text-[12px] font-black text-indigo-500 uppercase tracking-widest\">트랙 A 선택 시</p><ul class=\"space-y-1.5\"><li class=\"flex items-start gap-2 group cursor-default\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-check w-3 h-3 text-green-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0 transition-transform group-hover:scale-125\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg><span class=\"text-[12px] font-medium text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 group-hover:text-slate-800 dark:group-hover:text-slate-200 transition-colors leading-tight\">프론트/백엔드 연결 흐름 이해</span></li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-2 group cursor-default\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-check w-3 h-3 text-green-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0 transition-transform group-hover:scale-125\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg><span class=\"text-[12px] font-medium text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 group-hover:text-slate-800 dark:group-hover:text-slate-200 transition-colors leading-tight\">API 통신의 기본 원리 습득</span></li></ul></div><div class=\"h-[1px] bg-border\"></div><div class=\"space-y-2\"><p class=\"text-[12px] font-black text-teal-500 uppercase tracking-widest\">트랙 B 선택 시</p><ul class=\"space-y-1.5\"><li class=\"flex items-start gap-2 group cursor-default\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-check w-3 h-3 text-green-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0 transition-transform group-hover:scale-125\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg><span class=\"text-[12px] font-medium text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 group-hover:text-slate-800 dark:group-hover:text-slate-200 transition-colors leading-tight\">데이터베이스(DB) 핵심 개념</span></li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-2 group cursor-default\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-check w-3 h-3 text-green-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0 transition-transform group-hover:scale-125\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg><span class=\"text-[12px] font-medium text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 group-hover:text-slate-800 dark:group-hover:text-slate-200 transition-colors leading-tight\">CRUD 데이터 수명 주기 설계</span></li></ul></div><div class=\"h-[1px] bg-border\"></div><div class=\"space-y-2\"><p class=\"text-[12px] font-black text-orange-500 uppercase tracking-widest\">트랙 C 선택 시</p><ul class=\"space-y-1.5\"><li class=\"flex items-start gap-2 group cursor-default\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-check w-3 h-3 text-green-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0 transition-transform group-hover:scale-125\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg><span class=\"text-[12px] font-medium text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 group-hover:text-slate-800 dark:group-hover:text-slate-200 transition-colors leading-tight\">LLM 호출 아키텍처 파악</span></li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-2 group cursor-default\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-check w-3 h-3 text-green-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0 transition-transform group-hover:scale-125\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg><span class=\"text-[12px] font-medium text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 group-hover:text-slate-800 dark:group-hover:text-slate-200 transition-colors leading-tight\">API 기반 지능형 서비스 설계</span></li></ul></div></div></div></aside><div class=\"lg:col-span-9 space-y-16\"><div class=\"bg-card rounded-2xl border border-border p-8 shadow-sm space-y-12 transition-colors\"><div class=\"flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-start gap-4 pb-8 border-b border-border text-left\"><div class=\"space-y-3\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2\"><span class=\"bg-blue-100 text-blue-600 text-[12px] font-black px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full uppercase tracking-widest\">System &amp; Structure</span></div><h2 class=\"text-3xl font-black text-slate-800 dark:text-white tracking-tight\">2. 기초: 시스템 사고의 시작</h2><p class=\"text-blue-600 font-bold text-lg leading-relaxed max-w-2xl\">&quot;왜 결과가 달라지는지 이해하는 단계&quot;</p><p class=\"text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 text-sm\">AI가 결과를 만들어내는 기술적 배경과 데이터의 흐름을 학습합니다.<br/>구조를 이해하면 더 복잡하고 안정적인 서비스를 설계할 수 있습니다.</p></div></div><div id=\"core\" class=\"scroll-mt-32 space-y-6 text-left\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3\"><div class=\"w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-blue-50 dark:bg-blue-500/10 flex items-center justify-center text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-database\"><ellipse cx=\"12\" cy=\"5\" rx=\"9\" ry=\"3\"></ellipse><path d=\"M3 5V19A9 3 0 0 0 21 19V5\"></path><path d=\"M3 12A9 3 0 0 0 21 12\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"text-xl font-black text-slate-800 dark:text-white\">핵심 주제 (Common Core)</h3></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4\"><div class=\"bg-slate-50 dark:bg-white/5 p-5 rounded-2xl border border-slate-100 dark:border-white/5 hover:border-blue-500/30 transition-all flex items-start gap-4 group\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-check w-5 h-5 text-blue-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg><div><h4 class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800 dark:text-white mb-1 group-hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors\">서버 / 클라이언트 구조</h4><p class=\"text-[12px] text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 leading-relaxed\">요청(Request)과 응답(Response)의 기본 메커니즘 이해</p></div></div><div class=\"bg-slate-50 dark:bg-white/5 p-5 rounded-2xl border border-slate-100 dark:border-white/5 hover:border-blue-500/30 transition-all flex items-start gap-4 group\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-check w-5 h-5 text-blue-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg><div><h4 class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800 dark:text-white mb-1 group-hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors\">실행 환경 (로컬 vs 클라우드)</h4><p class=\"text-[12px] text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 leading-relaxed\">개발 환경과 배포 환경의 차이 및 에지 런타임 개념</p></div></div><div class=\"bg-slate-50 dark:bg-white/5 p-5 rounded-2xl border border-slate-100 dark:border-white/5 hover:border-blue-500/30 transition-all flex items-start gap-4 group\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-check w-5 h-5 text-blue-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg><div><h4 class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800 dark:text-white mb-1 group-hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors\">도메인 / DNS 설정</h4><p class=\"text-[12px] text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 leading-relaxed\">웹 사이트 주소의 원리와 도메인 네임 서버 연결 방법</p></div></div><div class=\"bg-slate-50 dark:bg-white/5 p-5 rounded-2xl border border-slate-100 dark:border-white/5 hover:border-blue-500/30 transition-all flex items-start gap-4 group\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-check w-5 h-5 text-blue-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg><div><h4 class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800 dark:text-white mb-1 group-hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors\">컨텍스트 &amp; 기억 구조</h4><p class=\"text-[12px] text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 leading-relaxed\">AI가 정보를 유지하는 방식(Window Context)과 한계</p></div></div><div class=\"bg-slate-50 dark:bg-white/5 p-5 rounded-2xl border border-slate-100 dark:border-white/5 hover:border-blue-500/30 transition-all flex items-start gap-4 group\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-check w-5 h-5 text-blue-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg><div><h4 class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800 dark:text-white mb-1 group-hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors\">에이전트 한계 (일관성 문제)</h4><p class=\"text-[12px] text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 leading-relaxed\">할루시네이션 및 비결정적 응답에 대응하는 전략</p></div></div><div class=\"bg-slate-50 dark:bg-white/5 p-5 rounded-2xl border border-slate-100 dark:border-white/5 hover:border-blue-500/30 transition-all flex items-start gap-4 group\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-check w-5 h-5 text-blue-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg><div><h4 class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800 dark:text-white mb-1 group-hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors\">아키텍처 다이어그램 기초</h4><p class=\"text-[12px] text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 leading-relaxed\">복잡한 시스템 구성을 한눈에 그리는 설계 기법</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"pt-4 border-t border-border text-left\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 mb-6\"><div class=\"w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-teal-50 dark:bg-teal-500/10 flex items-center justify-center text-teal-600 dark:text-teal-400\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-globe\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"M12 2a14.5 14.5 0 0 0 0 20 14.5 14.5 0 0 0 0-20\"></path><path d=\"M2 12h20\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"text-xl font-black text-slate-800 dark:text-white\">선택형 실습 트랙 (Optional Tracks)</h3></div><div class=\"space-y-12\"><div id=\"track-a\" class=\"scroll-mt-32 bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 rounded-3xl border-2 border-blue-100 dark:border-blue-500/20 p-8 space-y-6 hover:border-blue-500 transition-all group shadow-sm\"><div class=\"flex justify-between items-center\"><div class=\"inline-flex bg-blue-50 dark:bg-blue-500/10 text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 text-[12px] font-black px-3 py-1 rounded-full uppercase tracking-widest\">Track A</div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-xs font-bold text-slate-400\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-clock text-blue-400\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><polyline points=\"12 6 12 12 16 14\"></polyline></svg> 예상 70분</div></div><div><h4 class=\"text-2xl font-black text-slate-800 dark:text-white mb-2\">웹 구조 이해</h4><p class=\"text-sm text-slate-500 leading-relaxed\">프론트엔드와 백엔드가 어떻게 데이터를 주고받는지 실습합니다.</p></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 pt-2\"><div class=\"bg-slate-50 dark:bg-white/5 p-4 rounded-xl border border-slate-100 dark:border-white/5\"><p class=\"text-xs font-bold mb-2\">실습 01. 연결 흐름 분석</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-slate-500 leading-relaxed\">네트워크 탭을 통해 데이터가 오가는 전 과정을 모니터링합니다.</p></div><div class=\"bg-slate-50 dark:bg-white/5 p-4 rounded-xl border border-slate-100 dark:border-white/5\"><p class=\"text-xs font-bold mb-2\">실습 02. API 호출 미션</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-slate-500 leading-relaxed\">외부 API를 연동하여 실시간 데이터를 화면에 출력해봅니다.</p></div></div><button class=\"w-full py-4 bg-slate-900 dark:bg-white/10 text-white font-black rounded-2xl hover:bg-blue-600 transition-all\">웹 구조 실습 시작</button></div><div id=\"track-b\" class=\"scroll-mt-32 bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 rounded-3xl border-2 border-teal-100 dark:border-teal-500/20 p-8 space-y-6 hover:border-teal-500 transition-all group shadow-sm\"><div class=\"flex justify-between items-center\"><div class=\"inline-flex bg-teal-50 dark:bg-teal-500/10 text-teal-600 dark:text-teal-400 text-[12px] font-black px-3 py-1 rounded-full uppercase tracking-widest\">Track B</div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-xs font-bold text-slate-400\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-clock text-teal-400\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><polyline points=\"12 6 12 12 16 14\"></polyline></svg> 예상 90분</div></div><div><h4 class=\"text-2xl font-black text-slate-800 dark:text-white mb-2\">데이터 흐름</h4><p class=\"text-sm text-slate-500 leading-relaxed\">데이터의 저장, 수정, 삭제(CRUD) 과정을 설계하고 직접 구현합니다.</p></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 pt-2\"><div class=\"bg-slate-50 dark:bg-white/5 p-4 rounded-xl border border-slate-100 dark:border-white/5\"><p class=\"text-xs font-bold mb-2\">실습 01. DB 스키마 설계</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-slate-500 leading-relaxed\">효율적인 데이터 보관을 위한 테이블 구조를 AI와 함께 설계합니다.</p></div><div class=\"bg-slate-50 dark:bg-white/5 p-4 rounded-xl border border-slate-100 dark:border-white/5\"><p class=\"text-xs font-bold mb-2\">실습 02. CRUD 로직 구현</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-slate-500 leading-relaxed\">데이터베이스에 직접 접근하여 정보를 다루는 API를 제작합니다.</p></div></div><button class=\"w-full py-4 bg-slate-900 dark:bg-white/10 text-white font-black rounded-2xl hover:bg-teal-600 transition-all\">데이터 실습 시작</button></div><div id=\"track-c\" class=\"scroll-mt-32 bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 rounded-3xl border-2 border-orange-100 dark:border-orange-500/20 p-8 space-y-6 hover:border-orange-500 transition-all group shadow-sm\"><div class=\"flex justify-between items-center\"><div class=\"inline-flex bg-orange-50 dark:bg-orange-500/10 text-orange-600 dark:text-orange-400 text-[12px] font-black px-3 py-1 rounded-full uppercase tracking-widest\">Track C</div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-xs font-bold text-slate-400\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-clock text-orange-400\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><polyline points=\"12 6 12 12 16 14\"></polyline></svg> 예상 80분</div></div><div><h4 class=\"text-2xl font-black text-slate-800 dark:text-white mb-2\">AI 구조 이해</h4><p class=\"text-sm text-slate-500 leading-relaxed\">LLM API가 어떻게 작동하며 서비스와 어떻게 결합되는지 파악합니다.</p></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 pt-2\"><div class=\"bg-slate-50 dark:bg-white/5 p-4 rounded-xl border border-slate-100 dark:border-white/5\"><p class=\"text-xs font-bold mb-2\">실습 01. LLM API 핸들링</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-slate-500 leading-relaxed\">프롬프트를 API 파라미터로 전송하고 응답을 받는 구조를 실습합니다.</p></div><div class=\"bg-slate-50 dark:bg-white/5 p-4 rounded-xl border border-slate-100 dark:border-white/5\"><p class=\"text-xs font-bold mb-2\">실습 02. 서비스 파이프라인</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-slate-500 leading-relaxed\">사용자 입력부터 AI 처리, 최종 출력까지의 전체 흐름을 완성합니다.</p></div></div><button class=\"w-full py-4 bg-slate-900 dark:bg-white/10 text-white font-black rounded-2xl hover:bg-orange-600 transition-all\">AI 구조 실습 시작</button></div></div></div><div class=\"pt-8 border-t border-border flex justify-between\"><a href=\"/curriculum\"><button class=\"bg-slate-100 dark:bg-white/5 text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 px-8 py-3 rounded-xl font-bold flex items-center gap-2 hover:bg-slate-200 transition-all\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right w-4 h-4 rotate-180\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg> 1. 입문 단계로</button></a><a href=\"/curriculum/practice\"><button class=\"bg-slate-900 dark:bg-white/20 text-white px-8 py-3 rounded-xl font-bold flex items-center gap-2 hover:bg-emerald-600 transition-all shadow-lg hover:shadow-emerald-500/20\">3. 실전 단계: 프로덕트 빌딩 <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox